sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the SPDR Dow Jones Industrial Average ETF (Symbol: DIA) shows an impressive 11.3% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD), which makes up 4.94% of the SPDR Dow Jones Industrial Average ETF (Symbol: DIA), has seen 3 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $1,030,974,304 worth of HD, making it the #5 largest holding.
